tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE sales_data (
    sales_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    album_id INT,
    genre VARCHAR(50),
    total_sales DECIMAL,
    release_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE albums (
    album_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    album_name VARCHAR(100),
    genre_id INT,
    sales_total DECIMAL(10,2)
    FOREIGN KEY (genre_id) REFERENCES genres(genre_id)
);

CREATE TABLE albums (
    album_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    album_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    genre_id INT,
    album_sales INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (genre_id) REFERENCES genres(genre_id)
);

CREATE TABLE tracks (
    track_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    track_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    album_id INT,
    track_length INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (album_id) REFERENCES albums(album_id)
);

CREATE TABLE sales (
    sale_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    track_id INT,
    sale_date DATE,
    sale_amount INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (track_id) REFERENCES tracks(track_id)
);

CREATE TABLE albums (
  album_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  album_name VARCHAR(255),
  release_date DATE,
  genre VARCHAR(50),
  sales_amount DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE tracks (
  track_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  track_name VARCHAR(255),
  duration TIME,
  genre VARCHAR(50),
  album_id INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (album_id) REFERENCES albums(album_id)
);

CREATE TABLE sales (
  sale_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  sale_date DATE,
  album_id INT,
  quantity INT,
  total_price DECIMAL,
  FOREIGN KEY (album_id) REFERENCES albums(album_id)
);
